{"tid":1370780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［被屈三毛］你話我三毛乜都好，總之雙普選先係主菜","createTime":"2019-07-27T05:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:12:08.000Z","uid":149630,"like":27,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fa62cd173d536889cc331b0640f1ec85fb4457fa","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Q7UhW6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Q7UhW6.png&h=487e4e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個版本夠晒，唔好再亂加具體做法上去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吹風話我三毛<br />\n我都預左<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求前四項<br />\n都係為左維持民眾團結<br />\n民心歸向</span></span><br />\n唔需要set 任何具體點落實<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前四訴求<br />\n係為左運動燃料充足<br />\n運動曠日持久<br />\n直至政府跪低答應終極訴求<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">雙普選</span></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一第二個個訴求<br />\n林鄭回應左，我地都可以話未回應<br />\n話佢文字藝術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">正係因為我地無幫個訴求落過定義</span></strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家定義左點為之追究左黑警濫權<br />\n即係政權有方法去將訴求成就達成<br />\n點解要咁on9<br />\n<br />\n政府自己提出係一回事<br />\n點解要自己提咁on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">講具體方案只令我地無法將戰果最大化</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">被屈post </span></span></strong></ins><br />\n獨立調查委員會成立之日，就是運動面臨崩解之時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369716</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7258b796cad5b5d389c926794c653cc30b8aa537","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家定義左點為之追究左黑警濫權<br />\n即係政權有方法去將訴求<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">成就達成</span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"821e0d49639e4f65321b61cf87528187002abd2f","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9d47ef1c22df87d16031ab8e318e0e8d7df0298","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a80600299d8bcd603f2491cafcc8c70e18d07661","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51b6f631b595c473461bb8e71745da1dfa9ee840","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:56:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0560317d4a8e5ddbf038e9176f70243e8bbbaab","tid":1370780,"uid":279911,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"3毛就3毛啦。扮番中立。"},{"pid":"aaeb9e44d6b3a8071d98fa7482e62ca5b496e4aa","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"820f69314d0a6520baa7b00690a900298a8613a8","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72fd08f8a06383038c2f45fa3088abecc87908b6","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab1b47a590fa9b9bed7fe2024e96d8dd7d50fc64","tid":1370780,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2816132bac2f8bb0e1af37b57c5a26978f79dc2","tid":1370780,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8a016120b3a064f1efedced1cf19618e3a0e7e01","tid":1370780,"